title: Seitokaichou ni Chuukoku (Hey, Class President!)
synopsis: Even as he tries to keep the student council president out of trouble, Vice President Chiga-kun finds himself being drawn to the president's strength and power. Chiga-kun wonders how he, being such an intelligent individual, can be so unwillingly taken with a boy who is so country and simple...
staff: [['Kawakubo, Keiji', ['Director']], ['Monchi, Kaori', ['Original Creator']], ['Abe, Nobuyuki', ['Sound Manager']], ['Suzuki, Eri', ['Color Design']]]
